      "created": "2021-11-11T18:23:45.904+0000",
      "description": "In order to facilitate resource-aware Opportunistic container allocation, we will need to pass allocated container information to {{ClusterNode}}, which in turn gets its information from {{RMNode}}.\r\nHowever, {{RMNode}} currently only holds containers and node utilization based on the actual physical resource utilization, not at the allocated container level.\r\nThis sub-task aims to allow {{RMNode}} to be aware of all allocated resources on the node upon a node heartbeat.",
